abstract: n +1 singer reiterates corporate rating for redde .
article: redde 's stock had its `` corporate '' rating reaffirmed by n +1 singer in a research report issued on monday . separately , j p morgan chase & co lifted their price objective on redde from gbx 193 to gbx 197 and gave the stock an `` overweight '' rating in a research note on friday , september 8th . shares of redde opened at gbx 174.75 on monday . redde has a 52-week low of gbx 1.58 and a 52-week high of gbx 182 . copyright violation warning : this news story was originally posted by daily political and is the sole property of of daily political .
